{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/adjust-the-hover-state-of-an-anchor-tag","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"applied-visual-design","demoType":null,"title":"Prilagodi hover stanje anchor taga","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Ovaj izazov pokriva upotrebu pseudo-klasa. Pseudo-klasa je kljucna rec koja se moze dodati selektoru da bi se ciljalo posebno stanje elementa.</p>\n<p>Na primer, stil anchor taga moze da se promeni u hover stanju koriscenjem pseudo-klasnog selektora <code>:hover</code>. Ovo je CSS kod koji menja <code>color</code> anchor taga u crvenu boju tokom hover stanja:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\">a:hover {\n  color: red;\n}\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"587d781d367417b2b2512ac8","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>U editoru vec postoji CSS pravilo koje postavlja sve <code>a</code> tagove na crnu boju. Dodajte pravilo tako da kada korisnik predje misem preko <code>a</code> taga, <code>color</code> bude plava.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/c/cakRGcm","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301035,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/adjust-the-hover-state-of-an-anchor-tag"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\n  a {\n    color: #000;\n  }\n\n\n\n</style>\n<a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/\" target=\"_blank\">CatPhotoApp</a>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Boja anchor taga treba da ostane crna; dodajte samo CSS pravilo za <code>:hover</code> stanje.</p>","testString":"const anchorElement = document.querySelecto